OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780949162
OL,3,CCross-border project will bring
OL,4,Ctogether communities of Creeslough and
OL,5,CGreysteel
OL,7,FA new cross-border peace initiative
OL,8,Fwill bring together rural communities
OL,9,Fimpacted by tragedy in Creeslough and
OL,10,FGreysteel.
OL,12,FMore than 6.28 million euro (#5.43
OL,13,Fmillion) in Peaceplus funding has been
OL,14,Fawarded to the project, which will see
OL,15,Fthe installation of a 50,000 sq ft air
OL,16,Fdome facility at Greeysteel, Co
OL,17,FLondonderry, and the redevelopment of
OL,18,Fa "community shed" in Creeslough, Co
OL,19,FDonegal.
OL,26,@zD@COUzD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
