OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780949162
OL,3,CCross-border project will bring
OL,4,Ctogether communities of Creeslough and
OL,5,CGreysteel
OL,7,FMatthew Byrne, from the Creeslough
OL,8,FCommunity Association, said the award
OL,9,F"further recognises the trauma" that
OL,10,Fboth communities continue to
OL,11,Fexperience.
OL,13,FTen people were killed in an explosion
OL,14,Fat a service station in the village of
OL,15,FCreeslough on October 7 2022.
OL,17,FIn the village of Greysteel, eight
OL,18,Fcivilians, both Catholics and
OL,19,FProtestants, died when the Rising Sun
OL,20,Fbar in the Co Londonderry village was
OL,21,Fattacked on October 30 1993.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
