FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780949162
OL,3,CCross-border project will bring
OL,4,Ctogether communities of Creeslough and
OL,5,CGreysteel
OL,7,FSeven were killed on the night while
OL,8,Fthe eighth victim died several months
OL,9,Flater from their injuries.
OL,11,FOne of the UDA/UFF gunmen involved
OL,12,Fshouted "trick or treat" before
OL,13,Fpulling the trigger.
OL,15,FPeaceplus is managed by the Special EU
OL,16,FProgrammes Body (SEUPB) and represents
OL,17,Fa funding partnership between the
OL,18,FEuropean Union, the UK and Irish
OL,19,Fgovernments and the Northern Ireland
OL,20,FExecutive.
OL,26,@tD@IOUtD@XO]
