PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780949162
OL,3,CCross-border project will bring
OL,4,Ctogether communities of Creeslough and
OL,5,CGreysteel
OL,7,FThe funding has been awarded to the
OL,8,FGrowth (Growing Resilience,
OL,9,FOpportunities & Wellbeing, Through
OL,10,FHealing) project, a cross-border
OL,11,Finitiative designed to support rural
OL,12,Fregeneration, social inclusion and
OL,13,Fcommunity wellbeing in the two
OL,14,Fvillages.
OL,16,FThe funding of 6,281,679.68 euro will
OL,17,Fsupport community-led regeneration and
OL,18,Fshared activity in the rural
OL,19,Fcommunities.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780949162
OL,3,CCross-border project will bring
OL,4,Ctogether communities of Creeslough and
OL,5,CGreysteel
OL,7,FIt will focus on building
OL,8,Fcrosscommunity and crossborder
OL,9,Frelationships between Greysteel and
OL,10,FCreeslough.
OL,12,FPlans include the installation of a
OL,13,F50,000 sq ft air dome facility at the
OL,14,FVale Centre in Greysteel which will be
OL,15,Fused for shared health, recreational,
OL,16,Farts, cultural and tourism activities
OL,18,FIt will also see the redevelopment of
OL,19,Fa community shed in Creeslough for
OL,20,Fcommunity use and tourism-related
OL,21,Factivity.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780949162
OL,3,CCross-border project will bring
OL,4,Ctogether communities of Creeslough and
OL,5,CGreysteel
OL,7,FThere will also be a programme of
OL,8,Fengagement involving 3,230
OL,9,Fparticipants from the two villages,
OL,10,Ffocused on health and wellbeing, sport
OL,11,Fand physical activity and tourism
OL,12,Fpromotion.
OL,14,FThe project will be led by Greysteel
OL,15,FCommunity Enterprises Ltd, working in
OL,16,Fpartnership with Creeslough Community
OL,17,FAssociation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
