FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780949162
OL,3,CCross-border project will bring
OL,4,Ctogether communities of Creeslough and
OL,5,CGreysteel
OL,7,FNon-profit organisation Developing
OL,8,FHealth Communities (DHC) will assist
OL,9,Fboth communities in developing
OL,10,Fprogrammes grounded in trauma-informed
OL,11,Fpractice.
OL,13,FThe budget will see 4,985,527.90 euro
OL,14,Fallocated to Greysteel Community
OL,15,FEnterprises Ltd, 986,426.52 euro to
OL,16,FCreeslough Community Association, and
OL,17,F309,725.26 euro to DHC.
OL,19,FColumba Mailey from The Vale Centre
OL,20,Fsaid the funding would be a "game-
OL,21,Fchanger" for communities.
OL,26,@|D@]OU}D@HO]
