OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780949162
OL,3,CCross-border project will bring
OL,4,Ctogether communities of Creeslough and
OL,5,CGreysteel
OL,7,FHe said: "This investment will allow
OL,8,Fus to develop facilities and
OL,9,Fprogrammes that support wellbeing and
OL,10,Fbring people together in meaningful
OL,11,Fways.
OL,13,F"Our partnerships with Creeslough and
OL,14,FDHC are central to this, and we look
OL,15,Fforward to what we can achieve
OL,16,Ftogether."
OL,26,@oD@JOUuD@AOUxD@JO]
