SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780949162
OL,3,CCross-border project will bring
OL,4,Ctogether communities of Creeslough and
OL,5,CGreysteel
OL,7,FMr Byrne added: "This Peaceplus
OL,8,Ffunding further recognises the trauma
OL,9,Fthat the communities of both
OL,10,FCreeslough and Greysteel are going
OL,11,Fthrough.
OL,13,F"It will help to strengthen
OL,14,Frelationships as both communities
OL,15,Fshare experiences and help each other.
OL,17,F"The Greysteel community have already
OL,18,Fbeen so helpful and we look forward to
OL,19,Fworking further together to implement
OL,20,Fmore supports and initiatives."
OL,26,@oD@QOUuD@AOUyD@AOU|D@_O]
