OL,3,CCross-border project will bring
OL,4,Ctogether communities of Creeslough and
OL,5,CGreysteel
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland Agriculture,
OL,8,FEnvironment and Rural Affairs Minister
OL,9,FAndrew Muir said it was an "important
OL,10,Frural project".
OL,12,FHe said: "I am pleased that my
OL,13,Fdepartment is working in partnership
OL,14,Fwith the Department of Rural and
OL,15,FCommunity Development and the
OL,16,FGaeltacht and SEUPB to support this
OL,17,Fimportant investment."
OL,19,FIrish Minister for Rural and Community
OL,20,FDevelopment and the Gaeltacht, Dara
OL,21,FCalleary, also welcomed the project.
OL,26,@qD@\OUrD@NO]tD@JOUyD@VO]
