OL,3,CCross-border project will bring
OL,4,Ctogether communities of Creeslough and
OL,5,CGreysteel
OL,7,FHe said: "This undertaking will
OL,8,Fdeliver long-term benefits to the
OL,9,Farea."
OL,11,FIrish Minister of State with
OL,12,FResponsibility for Community
OL,13,FDevelopment and Charities Jerry
OL,14,FButtimer said: "This substantial
OL,15,Ffunding will make communal spaces and
OL,16,Fservices more accessible in rural
OL,17,Fareas."
