OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780949162
OL,3,CCross-border project will bring
OL,4,Ctogether communities of Creeslough and
OL,5,CGreysteel
OL,7,FSEUPB chief executive Gina McIntyre
OL,8,Fsaid: "By investing in shared spaces,
OL,9,Fcommunity-led initiatives and
OL,10,Fwellbeing-focused programmes, this
OL,11,Fproject will help create lasting
OL,12,Fpositive change and reinforce the
OL,13,Fvital role that collaboration plays in
OL,14,Fshaping vibrant and inclusive rural
OL,15,Fcommunities."
OL,26,@pD@GOUwD@MO]
