OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780949162
OL,3,CCross-border project will bring
OL,4,Ctogether communities of Creeslough and
OL,5,CGreysteel
OL,7,FEdel O'Doherty, from DHC, said: "As
OL,8,Fpart of the project, DHC will work
OL,9,Fclosely with local communities to
OL,10,Fdesign and deliver a broad programme
OL,11,Fof health and wellbeing initiatives,
OL,12,Fincluding mental health awareness and
OL,13,Ftrauma-informed training."
OL,15,FShe added: "Through this partnership,
OL,16,FDHC will help create safe, supportive
OL,17,Fspaces where individuals and
OL,18,Fcommunities can build resilience,
OL,19,Fstrengthen connections and improve
OL,20,Foverall wellbeing.
